Audit all app registrations with their permissions:
```python
def audit_apps(session):
    apps = graph_paginate(session, 'https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/applications', params={'$select': 'id,appId,displayName,requiredResourceAccess'})
    for app in apps:
        sp = get_sp_by_app_id(session, app['appId'])
        if sp:
            app['granted'] = get_granted_permissions(session, sp['id'])
    return apps
```
